<title>Easy Lunch Bowl</title>
<filename>easy_lunch_bowl.xml</filename>
<thumbnail>easy_lunch_bowl.jpeg</thumbnail>
<category>Lunch</category>
<category>Dinner</category>
<diet>GlutenFree</diet>
<diet>Vegetarian</diet>
<diet>EggFree</diet>
<yield>2</yield>
<prepTime>PT30M</prepTime>
<cookTime>PT10M</cookTime>
<ingredient>Cooked rice</ingredient>
<ingredient>Can lentils rinsed and drained</ingredient>
<ingredient>Kale washed stripped and chopped </ingredient>
<ingredient>Tzatziki</ingredient>
<ingredient>Sweet spud chopped and cooked</ingredient>
<ingredient>Salad- radish/tomatoes/celery </ingredient>
<step>In a bowl put a handful of kale.</step>
<step>On top pile a layer of rice, then pile sweet spud, lentil ( 1/4 cup), salad and tzatziki.</step>
<step>Serve cold and let the person mix together if they want.</step>
</recipe>

